00:02:07.885 --> 00:02:13.706
It's starting to turn into that time and the trees start to do their thing and they make my eyes water.

00:02:13.706 --> 00:02:22.960
But I'm not crying; they're burning from the trees and the cedars.

00:02:26.840 --> 00:02:35.599
I'll start off by just saying this: everything we say on the channel in word and indeed, we give all to the glory of God.

00:02:35.599 --> 00:02:36.093
Everything.

00:02:36.093 --> 00:02:43.520
And we're so grateful for the things that we have seen that are coming to pass, that the Lord is protecting people.

00:02:43.520 --> 00:02:49.359
And we prayed and we've stopped things, I believe by the hand of the Lord.

00:02:49.359 --> 00:02:54.400
And I'm so thankful for every single one of you that have come out and prayed with us.

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:57.050
I believe many hands make light work.

00:02:57.050 --> 00:03:07.173
We were so excited today when the Abraham Lincoln was protected and they saw the drone, and it was everything we were praying over.

00:03:07.173 --> 00:03:11.200
Now, would they have stopped it automatically without prayer?

00:03:11.200 --> 00:03:24.619
I believe prayer has a big role to play in everything, in protection of them not releasing anything out of that drone or whatever.

00:03:24.619 --> 00:03:35.240
I just think it's amazing to me whenever you see the things that you're praying over and it's the same battleship, it's the same everything, and everything falls down and they're protected.

00:03:38.470 --> 00:03:41.710
No men and women were hurt at all.

00:03:41.710 --> 00:03:44.770
And so, we continue to pray.

00:03:44.770 --> 00:03:47.966
I don't believe it's just a one-and-done.

00:03:53.479 --> 00:03:53.779
I believe this will be something that we need to continue to pray.

00:03:53.779 --> 00:03:58.319
It's not like, 'Well, we had one drone fall and it's over.

00:03:58.319 --> 00:04:10.560
' No, I saw that other boat out in the water be hit on the side of it.

00:04:16.384 --> 00:04:18.719
And then we've seen other things concerning the Iran escalation that I can't reveal publicly for protection for the people that are involved.

00:04:29.899 --> 00:04:30.189
I want to go over that and then I want to go over the third.

00:04:30.189 --> 00:04:31.349
Today's the third.

00:04:33.088 --> 00:04:36.987
And you know, you have people saying, 'Hey, you said a volcano was going off on the third.

