00:05:30.450 --> 00:05:37.440
I told Braden, I said it looks like I missed it.

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:45.990
And I'm going to be flat out with y'all.

00:05:45.990 --> 00:05:50.080
If I miss it, I apologize.

00:05:50.080 --> 00:05:58.700
