00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:21.620
And then, so what is it about the third and pride and the things that the Lord has showed me about President Trump having an arrogant heart?

00:06:21.620 --> 00:06:27.508
Venezuela being attacked on the 3rd of January, and I heard tres, tres, tres.

00:06:32.106 --> 00:06:32.520
And the Lord had us praying, interceding.

00:06:32.520 --> 00:06:37.199
It happened on the 3rd, but I specifically said February 3rd.

00:06:39.040 --> 00:06:41.760
So, we see February 3rd and here we are today.

00:06:47.639 --> 00:06:47.919
What happened today?

00:06:47.919 --> 00:06:50.729
