00:07:01.954 --> 00:07:14.330
Old alliances were, like I've said by the spirit of God, the old alliances were being rekindled from the 1960s Cuban missile crisis.

00:07:27.519 --> 00:07:27.839
And the Lord showed us that Russia would be flying.

00:07:27.839 --> 00:07:31.137
I saw biological things being stored in Cuba's island.

00:07:31.137 --> 00:07:40.400
But the Lord showed us that they would be liberated soon and that their government would fall.

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:49.407
Now, all the things that the Lord showed us, we've been praying over for a while.

00:07:49.407 --> 00:07:54.080
So, all of that's coming in the news today.

00:07:54.080 --> 00:07:57.919
Trump saying that they're running out of money.

00:07:57.919 --> 00:08:09.400
They only have a couple of weeks left of money and oil because of what we did.

00:08:09.400 --> 00:08:11.490
And we believe we can change all this.

00:08:11.490 --> 00:08:14.575
Now, Cuba says we want to have a meeting.

00:08:14.575 --> 00:08:20.630
So I said, 'Watch them in the secret of the night that they would try to attack us.

00:08:20.630 --> 00:08:23.279
' Russia's flying in planes.

00:08:23.279 --> 00:08:25.280
There's articles about it.

00:08:32.220 --> 00:08:32.480
And I thought, 'This is amazing.

00:08:32.480 --> 00:08:47.943
' So during this time frame about the third, going into the Olympics in three days, this is the time frame the Lord said in the two-week window there will be great decisions that President Trump will make and this will either make or break his term.

00:08:47.943 --> 00:08:51.110
But it's up to the church to pray.

00:08:51.110 --> 00:09:05.760
How will the church intercede for President Trump concerning his life, concerning protection for his family, concerning his presidency and the speeches that he'll make, concerning the Supreme Court justices, concerning the tariffs, who he chooses for...

00:09:05.760 --> 00:09:09.760
this is the week that he chose the new FED secretary?

00:09:16.658 --> 00:09:16.996
The money, the treasury, he picked the new guy.

00:09:16.996 --> 00:09:24.319
There's a lot of things that have happened this week, but was it to the extent of what I was expecting?

00:09:24.319 --> 00:09:27.120
I'm going to be flat real with y'all.

00:09:27.120 --> 00:09:30.230
No, I was expecting a lot more this week.

00:09:35.691 --> 00:09:41.110
The third where the fragrance comes up like the smell of feces.

00:09:41.110 --> 00:09:41.580
What is it?

00:09:44.399 --> 00:09:50.274
And I started studying what is it that would stink before the Father, and it's pride.

00:09:50.274 --> 00:10:16.766
There were so many things that were in what Dino was helping me with of what was an abomination to the Lord that would be a fragrance because there's so many things that have a fragrance that's good and a fragrance that's bad to the Father.

00:10:27.257 --> 00:10:27.600
And so the fragrances that are bad to the Father were pride and things like that.

00:10:27.600 --> 00:10:38.704
Fragrances that were good were like worship and things like that, and it's all in the Bible, in the Old Testament and the New Testament.

00:10:38.704 --> 00:10:46.720
So I want to go over what I said because, like I said, I don't brush it under the rug.

00:10:51.980 --> 00:10:52.270
