00:13:52.351 --> 00:14:01.250
I don't know why I'm seeing this, and she may not even be in Minnesota.

00:14:01.250 --> 00:14:03.839
Brandon, you're missing that page.

00:14:03.839 --> 00:14:18.034
I'm telling you, you know how when you start a hive and the bees start circling you, trying to sting you, and you start running?

00:14:18.034 --> 00:14:26.547
