00:21:28.628 --> 00:21:36.459
But I have a great urgency still in my spirit concerning the Valley of Decision, what he does with Iran and Cuba.

00:21:38.045 --> 00:21:45.399
In the middle of the night, I saw the planes coming in from China delivering weapons we've never seen before—laser weapons.

00:21:56.000 --> 00:21:56.390
