00:23:29.172 --> 00:23:29.546
You know, if your children were on there, if your husband or your wife was on there fighting, you would pray for them really hard, too.

00:23:47.120 --> 00:23:48.027
And I'm so thankful for every one of our servicemen and women, the people who put their life in danger every single day to keep our nation free.

00:23:48.027 --> 00:23:49.538
God bless you all.

00:23:56.480 --> 00:23:56.720
I mean, I can't imagine.

00:23:57.919 --> 00:24:08.418
