00:25:14.720 --> 00:25:14.900
You know what a hard job that is?

00:25:14.900 --> 00:25:32.571
And they don't make anything compared to some jobs, and it's just amazing because they're always on call and always on duty, and they do it because they love our nation.

00:25:53.440 --> 00:25:53.712
It is amazing.

00:25:53.712 --> 00:26:10.400
